name: Dboor-updated-v1.0
tagline: These files are completely useless before i do some updates.
body:
Original Files : https://github.com/Bazaid/tatar-wars-old

###All copyrights of old files goes to Dboor creators.

This project will be focused on updating these files for all PHP versions > 5.3  versions.
With more security , less memory usage, fixed bugs , this re-done, also few custom features.
(keep in mind that before any stable V1 Release commits can be done every minute).

###We still recruiting testing team , so if you interested contact me in email b.expire@gmail.com or skype : Jakbut

Please report all the bugs you can find, so they can be fixed faster. 
Live version of script will be available soon.
